description:
Still posting new content as of May 2023. Submit page reads the following;

*Getting featured is free but we have currently suspended free listings. We are reviewing backlog of hundreds of startup submissions. You can skip the waiting queue. We offer premium option if you want to get your startup featured within the next 48 hours and boosted on our social platforms.

Claims to have 100K followers. $99 might be a waste of money, we're not sure. We're not going to try, that's expensive for an unproven commodity.
